OL,3,CFan spending on Harry Styles Wembley
OL,4,Cgigs set to top #1bn
OL,6,FHarry Styles fans are expected to
OL,7,Fgenerate #1.1 billion during his
OL,8,Fupcoming 12-night residency at Wembley
OL,9,FStadium, according to new figures.
OL,11,FDespite ongoing cost-of-living
OL,12,Fpressures, the singer's "Together,
OL,13,FTogether" tour is set to bring a multi-
OL,14,Fmillion pound boost to the capital.
OL,16,FNew data from a Barclays survey
OL,17,Fsuggests that the average ticket-
OL,18,Fholder will spend #981 to attend the
OL,19,FLondon-exclusive shows. This includes
OL,20,Fthe cost of tickets, travel, overnight
OL,21,Fstays, and merchandise.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
