PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779196277
OL,3,CFan spending on Harry Styles Wembley
OL,4,Cgigs set to top #1bn
OL,6,FIt tops the average #848 spent by fans
OL,7,Fflocking to Taylor Swift's Eras Tour,
OL,8,Fas well as the #766 average for the
OL,9,FOasis Live '25 shows.
OL,11,FAs Styles' UK tour dates are strictly
OL,12,Flimited to London, many fans are
OL,13,Ffacing higher travel and accommodation
OL,14,Fcosts.
OL,16,FThey are also anticipated to spend an
OL,17,Faverage #102 on official tour
OL,18,Fmerchandise, while nine in 10 will
OL,19,Fparticipate in a "fan trend" on the
OL,20,Fday with 63% planning to wear a Harry
OL,21,FStyles-themed look.
OL,26,@{D@ROU{D@\O]
