OL,3,CFan spending on Harry Styles Wembley
OL,4,Cgigs set to top #1bn
OL,6,FA fifth will make sure their outfits
OL,7,Fare co-ordinated with their friends
OL,8,Fand 22% hope to create or exchange fan-
OL,9,Fmade items with other fans.
OL,11,FBarclays said the event was set to be
OL,12,Fa "major cultural moment" as a million
OL,13,Fticket-holders travel to London for
OL,14,Fthe 12 dates beginning on June 12.
OL,26,@tD@COUtD@YO]
