OL,3,CFan spending on Harry Styles Wembley
OL,4,Cgigs set to top #1bn
OL,6,FWith just one other European tour
OL,7,Flocation, in Amsterdam, Styles'
OL,8,FWembley residency will be the most
OL,9,Fperformances by any artist in a single
OL,10,Fyear at the venue, which has a
OL,11,Fcapacity of around 90,000 people for
OL,12,Fmusic events.
OL,14,FThe survey found those going to the
OL,15,Fshow spent an average of #143.20 on
OL,16,Ftheir ticket, with 19% saying this was
OL,17,Fmore than they planned but 66% saying
OL,18,Fthey would have been willing to pay
OL,19,Fmore if needed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
