OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779196277
OL,3,CFan spending on Harry Styles Wembley
OL,4,Cgigs set to top #1bn
OL,6,FOther expected costs include an
OL,7,Faverage #141.20 on accommodation,
OL,8,F#103.10 on transport and #103.10 on
OL,9,Ffood and drinks before the show.
OL,11,FTom Corbett, managing director of
OL,12,Fsponsorship and client experience at
OL,13,FBarclays, said: "This tour shows just
OL,14,Fhow powerful live entertainment can
OL,15,Fbe, benefiting consumers and
OL,16,Fbusinesses alike.
OL,26,@uD@QOU
