OL,3,CFan spending on Harry Styles Wembley
OL,4,Cgigs set to top #1bn
OL,6,F"'Concert tourism' is on the rise
OL,7,Fbecause of the extent to which people
OL,8,Fvalue unique, shared experiences ` so
OL,9,Fmuch so that they're willing to invest
OL,10,Fin them even when cutting back
OL,11,Felsewhere, and to travel to see their
OL,12,Ffavourite artists perform."
OL,14,FListen to the ITV News' entertainment
OL,15,Fpodcast, Unscripted.
